When they spotted the suspect, he tried to escape them towards the Canning River.
But he didn't get too far.
"He was standing in the water- saying 'I can't get out, come and get me'," said Senior Sergeant Shandell Castledine.
Constable Lachlan Perhavec wasn't too keen on getting his uniform wet, so he used a more reliable tactic - "A good cop negotiates".
"Sometimes people do funny things to try to get away," said Senior Sergeant Castledine.
