Matt Damon confronted African-American filmmaker Effie Brown during a discussion on diversity, saying it is not needed behind the scenes.
During an episode of Sunday Night of HBO's Project Greenlight, the veteran actor interrupted Brown when she stressed the need for alternative perspectives, in reference to a black protagonist in the project's chosen script.
