After the discussion aired, social media exploded with disapproval over Damon's comments.
Twitter user Mr Pooni expressed his anger at the clip, writing "Matt Damon is talking about the only black person in the room so he can explain diversity to her - that is SO WHITE it hurts."
The tweet earned more than 5,000 retweets and 4,000 likes since it was posted.
